Crazy
The Crazy is a warrior who has undergone Mind Over Matter (M.O.M.) cybernetic
implantation: metal spikes driven into the brain that unlock psionic energy
at the cost of sanity. Crazies are among the most physically dangerous
characters in the game, but they are unstable and prone to erratic behaviour.

Crazies gain ISP (psionic power) from their implants and combine this with
the physical enhancements of an elite soldier. They suffer random psychotic
episodes as a side effect of the procedure.

Attribute requirements: IQ 9, PS 10, PE 10.
ISP: Starting ISP pool from M.O.M. implants.
Starting equipment: M.O.M. implants (fitted), light body armour, two ranged
weapons, vibro-knife, and a personal sidearm.
